The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, epic
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, trance
2 different pets are kept: hamster, rat
1. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
2. the person eating orange is the owner of the hamster##1
3. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Food      | orange     | asparagus   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | action |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | trance |
| Pet           | hamster | rat    |

