The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, climbing
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
2. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |
| Food          | asparagus | cauliflower |
| Music-Genre   | metal     | folk        |
| Birthday           | february    | march      |
| Sport         | climbing  | basketball  |

